Terrorsaur/Rowdy Wolf:





Terrorsaur weived his way from the firepower from the two Dinobots. 
He laughed at their attempts. He aimed at Ultracon with his shoulder 
missiles and fired. He backed up at the same time he fired. 



Rowdy Wolf stepped out from the edge of the forest, clearly noticing 
the battle going on. He saw two Maximal Dinobots and the pterrorsaur 
he encountered earlier. 

"You bots and your pointless war!" he shouted. He aimed his right arm 
onto Dinotron, armed with the newly fixed cannon onto it. He fired an 
electronic blast at him from behind.
